included.description:
CoinDCX is on a mission to create world's most advanced and seamless trading experience. With the security of your assets and freedom to trade between maximum coin pairs as our main focus, we are designing the exchange platform to be a highly intuitive and delightful experience. 

I lead the product design and growth teams for the mission. I focus on creating a sustainable and trusted crypto community which together serves as a research ground for design. Every insight is then evaluated along with user behavioral data, psychology and heuristics to constantly build a better product which adapts to need of the market.
included.title: Product Design and Growth

included.description:
We're fueling a design revolution. We aim to help 500 businesses/startups double their revenue by 2020. We do that by using our unique design process that puts the focus back on user needs instead of crass assumptions of the team members. We use smart user research methods, advanced user behavioral data analysis, and user psychology to design an engaging and delightful experience for your product/business. 

We then take all that we learn from creating these awesome products and share it with our design community. We reveal all the (apparent) secrets behind designing world-class products. We also create physical design tools under our brand, THE NICHE MIND, those aid designers to create the next disruption.
included.title: Founder and CEO

included.description: We help businesses create successful marketing and sales strategies. Our predictable prospecting engine helps them automate their marketing campaigns and optimise them for best possible results. Apart from marketing automation we help them in Product Design and creating successful Sales Funnels for their product.
included.title: Chief Technology Officer

included.description:
Homebuying is a complex process, involving thousands of micro-decisions to be made by a User. We at HDFC RED help users take this decision in the most delightful and efficient way. 

I lead the product design team which was responsible for User Research, UX, UI and Behaviour Analysis for all the products across HDFC RED portfolio. I worked closely with the data analytics team to perform tests on the product with a goal increase the conversions.
included.title: Product Design Head

included.summary:
UI/UX Designer & Growth Hacker with 5 years of experience in helping over 45 startups across India, USA and Australia. Specialising in designing delightful experiences for digital products that knit closely with the business goals using conversion optimisation, lean data-driven design, rapid prototyping and user research. 
Specialities:
User Experience Design (UX), Design Strategy, Project Management, User Research, User Centered Process, Interviewing users, Persona Building, Information Architecture, Wireframing / Prototyping, Usability Analysis, Web/ Mobile Design, User Behaviour Analysis, Data Analytics, Sales Funnels and CRO. 
Developed 10 Mobile Apps and numerous websites for clients or otherwise.
